cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

The paper deals with deep learning methods for medical imaging segmentation, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). The use of self-ensembling is a specific technique that falls under the category of unsupervised learning (cs.NE) and the application to medical imaging is a specific domain (cs.MM).
